# Wedding Website - Cursor Rules

## Project Overview
This is a wedding invitation website for Deyaneira & Aaron's destination wedding in Puerto Rico on July 18, 2026. The site embodies tropical sophistication with a Bad Bunny "Debí Tirar Más Fotos" aesthetic - warm, nostalgic, and celebratory.

## Tech Stack
- **Framework:** Vite + React + TypeScript
- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS (custom palette)
- **Animations:** Framer Motion
- **Forms:** Google Sheets integration (NOT localStorage/sessionStorage)
- **Fonts:** Playfair Display (names), Montserrat (headings), Inter (body)

