## Special Considerations

### Envelope Animation
- Must feel like opening a real wedding invitation envelope
- Smooth, elegant, cinematic
- No information leaks before opening
- Letters "D & A" must be clearly visible when revealed
- Scroll must be completely blocked until revealed
- localStorage check to skip animation for returning visitors

### Mobile Experience Priority
- Most guests will view on mobile phones
- Touch interactions must feel natural
- No pinch-to-zoom needed (viewport meta tag)
- Fast loading on cellular connections

### Cultural Context
- Puerto Rican destination wedding
- Tropical sophistication (not touristy)
- Bad Bunny aesthetic (nostalgic, emotional, proud)
- Sunset/atardecer theme
- Family-oriented but adults-only event

## When in Doubt
- Prioritize elegance over complexity
- Choose subtle over flashy
- Favor white space over density
- Keep interactions smooth and natural
- Make it work perfectly on mobile first
- Remember: this is for a special moment in people's lives